  "display_fullname": "Stalker Melee Spines Impale",
  "display_help": "You can throw a single large Spine at a targeted foe. This Spine does only moderate damage, but carries a large amount of the Spine toxin. A successful attack can completely Immobilize most foes, as well as Slowing them, reducing their regeneration, and dealing Toxic poison damage for a long duration that starts strong and decays over time. Impale can also bring down flying entities.",
